lients, Informers, Listers, Fake clients) for both AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` | Full reference of all pkg types including workloadmanager, store, GVRs, HTTP routes, CLI flags (475 lines) |\n| `testing/agentcube_tdd_manifest.md` | TDD manifest defining required test cases per module |\n| `test_spec.md` | TDD specification with test case IDs (WM-001 through SDK-002) |\n| `.sdd_prompt.md` | The prompt used to generate the AR-002 design document |\n| `project.md` | Project overview: architecture, tech stack, conventions |\n\n---\n\n## 6. All Files Mentioning \"CodeInterpreter\" / \"codeinterpreter\" / \"code-interpreter\"\n\nFound **435 matches** across these files:\n\n| File | Match Count | Context |\n|------|-------------|---------|\n| `changes/AR-002/tasks.md` | ~40 | Task definitions for CodeInterpreter types |\n| `changes/AR-002/design.md` | ~80 | Full design specification |\n| `changes/AR-002/proposal.md` | ~30 | Proposal with type definition summary |\n| `changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md` | ~30 | Gherkin requirements |\n| `changes/AR-001/design.md` | ~15 | References CodeInterpreter as shared types |\n| `changes/AR-001/tasks.md` | ~10 | Tasks mentioning CodeInterpreter shared types |\n| `changes/AR-001/proposal.md` | ~3 | Mentions CodeInterpreter as future work |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | ~20 | Type definitions |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types_test.go` | ~30 | Unit tests |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | ~6 | Kind constants |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register_test.go` | ~8 | GVK/GVR tests |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info_test.go` | ~8 | Scheme registration tests |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | ~40 | DeepCopy methods |\n| `deployment/client-go.md` | ~20 | Generated client documentation |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/design.md` | ~30 | Reference of all types and GVRs |\n| `.sdd_prompt.md` | ~5 | SDD prompt context |\n\n---\n\n## 7. Existing pkg/apis Structure\n\n```\npkg/\n└── apis/\n    └── runtime/\n        └── v1alpha1/\n            ├── doc.go                          # +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package, +groupName\n            ├── groupversion_info.go            # GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, AddToScheme\n            ├── groupversion_info_test.go       # Scheme registration tests\n            ├── register.go                     # Kind constants, Resource() helper\n            ├── register_test.go                # GVK/GVR constant tests\n            ├── agent_type.go                   # AgentRuntime CRD (AR-001)\n            ├── agent_type_test.go              # AgentRuntime tests\n            ├── codeinterpreter_types.go        # CodeInterpreter CRD + shared types (AR-002)\n            ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go   # CodeInterpreter tests\n            └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go        # Auto-generated DeepCopy for ALL types\n```\n\n**Two CRDs in one API group:**\n1. **AgentRuntime** -- generic AI agent sandbox, uses embedded `corev1.PodSpec`\n2. **CodeInterpreter** -- code interpreter specific, uses flat `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`\n\n**Shared types** (defined in `codeinterpreter_types.go`, used by both CRDs):\n- `ProtocolType` (enum: HTTP, HTTPS)\n- `AuthModeType` (enum: picod, none) -- CodeInterpreter specific\n- `TargetPort` struct\n\n---\n\n## 8. Makefile / CRD Generation Scripts\n\n**No Makefile was found** in the project root. However, the design documents extensively reference the following generation toolchain:\n\n### Tools Referenced (from design docs):\n\n| Tool | Version | Purpose |\n|------|---------|---------|\n| `controller-gen` | v0.17.2 | DeepCopy method generation + CRD YAML generation |\n| `k8s.io/code-generator` | v0.34.1 | client-go code generation (Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake) |\n\n### Referenced Make Targets (from design docs, NOT present in repo):\n\n| Target | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `make generate` | Runs `controller-gen object paths=\"./pkg/apis/...\"` to produce `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` |\n| `make gen-crd` | Runs `controller-gen crd` to produce CRD YAML in `manifests/charts/base/crds/` |\n| `make gen-client` | Runs `hack/update-codegen.sh` to generate client-go code |\n| `make gen-all` | Runs `generate` + `gen-client` |\n\n### Generation Script (referenced but not present):\n- `hack/update-codegen.sh` -- uses `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 with `--with-watch` flag, output package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n\n### Pre-generated client-go Code (documented but not in repo):\nThe file `deployment/client-go.md` documents a complete `client-go/` directory structure that would be generated, including:\n- `clientset/versioned/` -- Clientset, scheme, fake clientset\n- `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/` -- AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface, fake clients\n- `informers/externalversions/` -- SharedInformerFactory, per-type informers\n- `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/` -- AgentRuntimeLister, CodeInterpreterLister\n\n---\n\n## Key Patterns and Conventions\n\n1. **API Group Naming:** `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` (domain: volcano.sh, project: agentcube, component: runtime)\n2. **Version:** `v1alpha1` (only version currently defined)\n3. **Module Path:** `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n4. **Package Layout:** `pkg/apis/{group}/{version}/` (standard Kubernetes convention)\n5. **Scheme Registration:** Uses `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme` Builder pattern\n6. **Code Generation Markers:** kubebuilder-style (`+kubebuilder:*`, `+k8s:*`, `+genclient`)\n7. **JSON Tags:** camelCase throughout\n8. **Go Structs:** PascalCase\n9. **DeepCopy Generation:** `controller-gen object` produces `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` with build tag `!ignore_autogenerated`\n10. **Test Framework:** `github.com/stretchr/testify/assert`\n11. **Change Request Process:** AR-XXX numbering, with proposal.md -> design.md -> tasks.md -> delta-spec.md workflow\n12. **Stage Naming:** ST-1 (Proposal), ST-3 (Design Complete), ST-4 (Implementation)\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28979e7b1ffecIe1tFJEtP4S01","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775809992776,"end":1775810160969}}}}
